3. BI Dashboards (Mockup Descriptions)


⭐ Dashboard 1: Executive Fraud Summary

Total fraud cases today

High-risk transactions trend (line chart)

Top 5 most flagged users (bar chart)

Alerts by risk level (pie chart)

⭐ Dashboard 2: Transaction Behavior Dashboard

Hourly transaction heatmap

Average transaction amount per user

High-value transaction counts

Suspicious nighttime activity (after 10 PM)

⭐ Dashboard 3: System Compliance Dashboard

Weekday/Holiday DML violations (bar chart)

Audit log summary

Trigger activity report

Number of blocked operations per user
